cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper is about age estimation using computer vision techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method also involves probabilistic modeling and learning, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The experiments are conducted on image datasets, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper also discusses the potential applications of age estimation in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
